---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Victor Augusteo"
  description="About Victor Augusteo - Head of Engineering at Boon AI"
>
  <div class="about-page">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <div class="content prose">
      <p>
        Hi! I'm Victor, currently Head of Engineering at Boon AI. I previously
        worked at Apple on various iOS projects.
      </p>

      <p>
        I write about travels with my family, technology & AI, books I've read,
        and the occasional philosophical rambling. This blog is my corner of the
        internet where I share my thoughts and experiences.
      </p>

      <h2>What I Write About</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Travels</strong> - Adventures with my family around the world</li>
        <li><strong>Tech</strong> - Software engineering, AI, and technology thoughts</li>
        <li><strong>Books</strong> - Reviews and summaries of books I've read</li>
        <li><strong>Philosophy</strong> - Occasional ramblings about life and meaning</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Connect</h2>

      <p>
        You can find me on <a href="https://twitter.com/AugusteoVictor" target="_blank">Twitter</a> or
        <a href="https://github.com/nicnocquee" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
  }

  .about-page h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-hand);
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .content {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
</style>
